title: Nylon Lazy Spoon and Ladle Set of 2
description: Super clever and convenient, Rachael Ray has made Jonathan's Lazy Spoons colorful and dishwasher safe! These clever tools are notched to rest on your pot's edge so drips stay in the pan, not on your countertop. Made of comfortable silicone, they are heat safe up to 500 degrees.
